{
  "texts": [
    "Ethical clearance was obtained from the University of South Africa (Reference: 2023/04/12/90501543/08/AM).",
    "Ethical considerations, including informed consent, privacy, anonymity, and confidentiality, were meticulously observed throughout the data collection phase.",
    "Although data collection occurred online, with no physical interaction between the researcher and the participants, the researchers, via the provided link containing the interview questions, furnished participants with details about the study objectives.",
    "Furthermore, background information outlining the significance of the study was presented.",
    "Additionally, the researchers assured the participants that the information gathered would be utilised for academic purposes."
  ]
}